snippet.title: Master System Longplay [101] Sitio do Picapau Amarelo
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: ConjiComani

One of the last games released, coming out in 1997. Based off a series of children's books by Monteiro Lobato. I play both Pedrinho's and Emilia's game, which are both slightly different. -
Disclaimer: Most videos by World of Longplays use SaveStates!
